node.text: This just in! Beginning August 9, the Disney Dream will kick off our long-awaited return to cruising with three- and four-night cruises from Port Canaveral, Florida. node.text: Just in time for the Oct. 1 start of “The World’s Most Magical Celebration” at @WaltDisneyWorld Resort, visitors to Orlando International Airport will be able to discover exciting Disney touches and new EARidescent magic as part of a wide-spanning art installation including images of favorite Disney characters on the terminal train stations, immersive photo ops with pop-up ride vehicles and a glistening glow of pixie dust to start making special memories as they pass through the airport. Learn more on the Disney Parks Blog (link in bio). #DisneyWorld50
